**/node_modules
# Agent worktrees are full checkouts of this repo. Without this, a worktree
# left on disk makes `pnpm format:check` fail on a second copy of every
# generated file — a confusing local-only red that CI never sees.
.claude/worktrees
**/dist
**/build
**/.output
**/.nuxt
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/storybook-static
packages/api-client-ts/src/generated
# dart-dio generates straight into the package root (see #168). These are all
# generator output — regenerated by `pnpm spec:codegen`, never hand-formatted.
# The hand-authored pubspec.yaml / .openapi-generator-ignore stay Prettier-managed.
packages/api-client-dart/lib
packages/api-client-dart/doc
packages/api-client-dart/test
packages/api-client-dart/README.md
packages/api-client-dart/analysis_options.yaml
packages/specs/dist
apps/mobile/.dart_tool
apps/mobile/build
apps/mobile/ios
apps/mobile/android
pnpm-lock.yaml

# Centrifugo config template carries `${VAR}` placeholders that envsubst
# expands at boot — Prettier's JSON parser rejects them.
docker/centrifugo/config.template.json

# Long-form prose — Markdown tables/prose fight Prettier's reflow and the
# churn isn't worth gating. `.impeccable/` holds generated design-critique
# dumps that regenerate unformatted anyway.
docs
.impeccable

# Superpowers scratch (plans, briefs, agent reports, progress ledger). Local
# working notes, git-ignored, regenerated per session — CI never sees them but
# they made `pnpm format:check` noisy locally.
.superpowers
